a simulated crosscountry ski unit in one corner of the flat rock 
plants fitness center 
job one the first mazda car made at flat rock rolled off 
the assembly line in september in november the company opened the 
1 million fitness center in a 90000squarefoot section of one of 
the plant buildings 
fitness programs once the reserve of management are moving 
from the front office to the plant floor at many companies said 
